    cost by 4.\n[On Play] [When Digivolving] Suspend 1 of your opponent's Digimon
    or Tamers. Then, 1 of their Digimon or Tamers can't unsuspend until their turn
    ends.\n[Your Turn] [Once Per Turn] When your Digimon are played or digivolve,
    if any of them have the [WG]\_trait, 2 of your Digimon may DNA digivolve into
    a [WG]\_trait Digimon card in the hand."
